          MODULE=elmo
         VERSION=1.3.2
          SOURCE=$MODULE-$VERSION.tar.gz
      SOURCE_URL=$SFORGE_URL/$MODULE
      SOURCE_VFY=sha1:d4e7999ce85c17df082a016fd70ee4978cfe1043
        WEB_SITE=http://elmo.sourceforge.net
         ENTERED=20040420
         UPDATED=20101111
           PSAFE=no
           SHORT="A feature-rich, highly configurable and fast mail client"

cat << EOF
Elmo is a feature-rich, highly configurable and fast mail client. You could
call it a Mail User Agent, but it offers much more than traditional MUA's.
A summary of its features:
  SMTP support (with authentication support)
  POP3 support
  a Bayesian mail filter!
  an address-book
  colors
  threads
  keymaps and hooks
  maildir and (partial) mbox support
  MIME support (including support for encoded headers)
Don't forget to launch elmoconf.pl to configure your box!
EOF
